law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 414, sec. 22, effective July 15, 1998. -- Repealed, reenacted, and amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 105, sec. 45, effective July 14 ,1992; and amended ch. 360, sec. 17, effective July 14 ,1992. -- Created 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 123, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1988.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/14/92). This section was amended by two 1992 Acts. Where those Acts are not in conflict, they have been compiled together. Where a conflict exists, Acts ch. 105 prevails pursuant to section 79 of that Act.
